      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a documented rear subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve adjustment to ensure optimal cam timing and compression. While the exterior shows minor road-rash consistent with spirited use, the mechanical integrity is top-tier for a driver-focused enthusiast.",
